message.content:
Nceda ukufakela phakathi kwexesha lokunciphisa lesoftware:

1. Qoqa "Start" kwi-Menyu yomqulu wesandla sakho.
2. Qoqa "Control Panel" ukuze uye kwi-Control Panel.
3. Qoqa "Programs" ukuze uye kwi-Programs.
4. Qoqa "Uninstall a Program" ukuze uye kwi-Uninstall a Program.
5. Qoqa "Software" ukuze ubuke iimfanelo zonke ezifanelekile zokulawula imoto.
6. Qoqa nge-imeyile ukuze ubekelele ngokwenene iimfanelo zokusebenzisa. 

Nceda ukhangela ngale ngxelo ukuba ungayenza kanjani nakwimfanelo zokulawula imoto.
